note: hi there, this is lunatic. i enjoy the moon, dancing to techno music, the desert ~ preferably all at the same time. i love riding bicycles. i drink a lot of puerh tea. i enjoy cooking tasty food. i like tinkering with computer stuff. i start many projects and finish few. i wish we didn't have to live together under the rule of capitalism but were rather associated as individual and truly free human beings. i am anti-fascist.
